{"title":"人在跃进歌唱中","authors":["邵宇"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在跃进歌唱中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者附记：画家邵宇同志参加中国文联参观团访问河北省张家口专区，这是他在涿鹿、怀来等地画的速写。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在涿鹿县劈山大渠指挥部门前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁担不长七尺三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小箩筐柳条编，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你甭小看这玩意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天挑走两座山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（民歌）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涿鹿硫磺化肥厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涿鹿有个化肥厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白手起家炼硫磺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有宿舍地是炕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不懂技术去拜访；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑水、烧饭、通讯员……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂长一人来充当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在高炉平地起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼出硫磺放金光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千方百计办工业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地方工业好榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建新村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官厅湖南花园乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子越过越兴旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧村尽在花果中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新村又起水库旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业社的技术中学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产技术要革命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村社社办学校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革命打先锋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长町村中的一面墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年干劲赛赵云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮年力气赛武松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年儿童像罗成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人干活似黄忠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部策划胜诸葛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女赛过穆桂英。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（民歌）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀来县南水泉村的早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早上工，晚下工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要和太阳比英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下地去耕种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果园去杀虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进诗歌写满墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在跃进歌唱中。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}